p.k: Robin tries to teach the Titans valuable life lessons by reading them fairytales but the others co-opt his stories and spin them into their own twisted yarns. / Brother Blood takes the Titans to trial for their recent destruction of Jump City. / After the other Titans are injured Beast Boy donates his blood to save them. / The Titans' Halloween party is interupted by the Hive Five robbing a candy factory. / It's Beast Boy's birthday! But will the other Titans remember?
